<%- include('../partials/head', { title, active }) %>
<%- include('../partials/nav', { user, active }) %>
<section class="panel">
  <div class="panel-title"><h1>SDE 资料库</h1><span>当前：<%= sdeCounts.types %> types / <%= sdeCounts.systems %> systems / <%= sdeCounts.blueprints %> blueprints</span></div>
  <form id="sde-search" class="toolbar"><input name="q" placeholder="搜索 type/system/blueprint"><select name="collection"><option value="types">Types</option><option value="systems">Solar Systems</option><option value="blueprints">Blueprints</option></select><select name="kind"><option value="">全部种类</option><option value="ship">ship</option><option value="module">module</option><option value="ore">ore</option><option value="mineral">mineral</option><option value="salvage">salvage</option><option value="data">data</option></select><button class="button small">搜索</button></form>
  <div id="sde-results" class="sde-table"></div>
</section>
<section class="panel rich-text">
  <h2>导入说明</h2>
  <p>下载官方 JSON Lines SDE 或使用 EVE-China/sde 脚本得到 JSONL，解压到服务器目录后执行：<code>npm run import:sde -- --dir ./sde-jsonl</code>。管理员也可以进入 <a href="/admin/sde">/admin/sde</a> 填写服务器路径导入。</p>
</section>
<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
